## User Review Required

> [!CAUTION]
> **Auto-Trading**: The app will include a button to **automatically execute trades** on the user's Binance account to match the AI-recommended allocation. This requires explicit user confirmation + PIN/biometric before every trade execution. Is this the behavior you want, or should it be read-only initially?

> [!WARNING]
> **Binance Testnet vs Production**: For development and initial deployment, I recommend using **Binance Testnet** (fake money) to avoid any accidental real trades. The app will have a toggle to switch between testnet and production. Confirm?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Backend Storage**: The current backend uses **in-memory storage** for users (`_users_db = {}`). For government-level production, this needs to be replaced with a proper database (PostgreSQL/Supabase). Should I also upgrade the backend storage as part of this plan, or keep it separate?

