## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph MobileApp["React Native App (Expo)"]
        direction TB
        S1[Onboarding + Auth] --> S2[Binance Connection]
        S2 --> S3[DAQ Questionnaire]
        S3 --> S4[AI Pipeline Execution]
        S4 --> S5[Dashboard + Portfolio]
        S5 --> S6[Analytics + Reports]
        S5 --> S7[Auto-Rebalance]
    end

    subgraph Backend["FastAPI Backend (Python)"]
        A1["/api/auth"] --> A2["/api/portfolio"]
        A2 --> A3["/api/daq"]
        A3 --> A4["/api/dashboard"]
        A4 --> A5["/api/portfolio/rebalance"]
    end

    subgraph Engine["4-Agent Intelligence Pipeline"]
        AG1["Agent 1: Macro Intel<br/>(HMM + RF + LLM)"]
        AG2["Agent 2: Behavioral<br/>(Dynamic Questions + ML Risk)"]
        AG3["Agent 3: Optimizer<br/>(Mean-Var + MonteCarlo + LLM)"]
        AG4["Agent 4: CRO Supervisor<br/>(Risk Audit + Safety)"]
        AG1 --> AG2 --> AG3 --> AG4
    end

    subgraph External["External APIs"]
        B[Binance API]
        TD[TwelveData]
        FR[FRED]
        GM[Google Gemini]
    end

    MobileApp -->|REST API| Backend
    Backend --> Engine
    Engine --> External
    Backend -->|Direct| B
```

