## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Justification |
|-------|-----------|---------------|
| **Framework** | Expo SDK 52 + React Native | Cross-platform (iOS + Android), government-standard |
| **Language** | TypeScript (strict) | Type safety, catches bugs at compile time |
| **Navigation** | Expo Router v4 | File-based routing, deep linking |
| **Animations** | React Native Reanimated 3 | 60fps native animations, smooth UX |
| **Charts** | react-native-svg + react-native-chart-kit | Allocation pie, equity curves, gauges |
| **HTTP Client** | Axios | Interceptors for JWT, retry logic |
| **Secure Storage** | expo-secure-store | Encrypted token + API key storage |
| **Biometrics** | expo-local-authentication | FaceID / Fingerprint |
| **State** | React Context + useReducer | Lightweight, no external deps |
| **Haptics** | expo-haptics | Tactile feedback on actions |
| **Blur** | expo-blur | Glassmorphism effects |
| **Gradients** | expo-linear-gradient | Premium gradient backgrounds |
| **Icons** | @expo/vector-icons (Ionicons) | Consistent icon set |

