### Backend Enhancements

#### [NEW] [rebalance.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/api/routes/rebalance.py)
New endpoint `POST /api/portfolio/rebalance` that:
1. Takes the latest Agent 3/4 recommended allocation
2. Compares with current Binance holdings
3. Calculates required trades
4. Executes trades (with user confirmation token)

#### [MODIFY] [server.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/api/server.py)
- Register the new rebalance router
- Add mobile app origins to CORS

