## User Flow (End-to-End)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant App as React Native App
    participant API as FastAPI Server
    participant P as Pipeline (4 Agents)
    participant B as Binance API

    Note over U,B: First-Time Setup
    U->>App: Open App → Onboarding
    U->>App: Register (email + password)
    App->>API: POST /api/auth/register
    API-->>App: JWT Token
    App->>App: Store token securely

    U->>App: Enter Binance API Keys
    App->>API: POST /api/portfolio/connect-binance
    API->>B: Validate keys
    B-->>API: Account info
    API-->>App: Connected ✅

    Note over U,B: AI Portfolio Analysis
    U->>App: Tap "Start AI Advisor"
    App->>API: POST /api/daq/start
    API->>P: Run Agent 1 (Macro Intel)
    P-->>API: Market context + Questions
    API-->>App: 4 scenario questions

    U->>App: Answer 4 questions
    App->>API: POST /api/daq/submit
    API->>P: Agent 2 (Profile) → Agent 3 (Optimize) → Agent 4 (Audit)
    P-->>API: Full pipeline results
    API-->>App: Portfolio recommendation

    App->>App: Show Dashboard with allocation

    Note over U,B: Auto-Rebalance (Optional)
    U->>App: Tap "Rebalance Portfolio"
    App->>API: POST /api/portfolio/rebalance
    API->>B: Calculate + Execute trades
    B-->>API: Trade confirmations
    API-->>App: Rebalance complete ✅
```

