### Browser-Based Testing
Using the Expo web preview (`npx expo start --web`), I will use the browser tool to:
1. Verify all screens render correctly
2. Walk through the complete user flow (register → connect → DAQ → dashboard)
3. Verify API calls are made correctly
4. Check responsive layout and animations

### Manual Verification
Please test on a physical device using Expo Go:
1. Install Expo Go from Play Store / App Store
2. Scan the QR code from `npx expo start`
3. Walk through: Onboarding → Register → Connect Binance (testnet) → Complete DAQ → View Dashboard
4. Verify animations are smooth (60fps)
5. Verify Binance balances show correctly
6. Verify AI pipeline executes and shows results

